text:
Just added <https://github.com/pilgr/Paper> and proguard is not working. Multiple warnings "Warning:there were 3 unresolved references to classes or interfaces." and exception "Warning:Exception while processing task java.io.IOException: Please correct the above warnings first.".

I have added the proguard config for paper <https://github.com/pilgr/Paper/blob/master/paperdb/proguard.txt> but still no avail.

text: For someone who reads it later, Adding "-dontwarn sun.misc.Unsafe" worked. One of the warnings was - "Warning:org.objenesis.instantiator.sun.UnsafeFactoryInstantiator: can't find referenced class sun.misc.Unsafe"
